metadata.name: Thirteen Visions
metadata.description:
Carrés (squares) is an exploration in colors, shapes and negative space. 

"Thirteen Visions" is the genesis piece in SERIES ONE, and is comprised of 13 different illustrations representing space, time and movement. 

Each series in Carrés has an overarching theme. SERIES ONE is all "Spaces and Places" and will contain 5 1/1s.
